data.description: Adorable 2/1 bungalow on over an acre of country living. The beautiful yard can be seen from the comfort of a front porch chair. Circular driveway with a detached carport and shed. The back yard is fenced in with a cozy burn pit. And room for your chickens. Enjoy entertaining on the large back porch. And the great functioning layout of the updated home. Separate dinning space, flex/office area. Recently updated galley kitchen leading to every space you could be entertaining in. Must see to appreciate.
